  "texts": [
    "To synthesize the current scenario of STEM TPD initiatives in China, this study undertakes a comprehensive review of the empirical research focusing on K-12 STEM TPD programs catalogued in the Web of Science (WOS), Google Scholar, Science Research Gate, CNKI, other Chinese search engines (Baidu Scholar, CQVIP, Wanfang Data, and VIP Fig. 11 The main findings of the reviewed studies.",
    "HUMANITIES AND SOCIAL SCIENCES COMMUNICATIONS | https://doi.org/10.1057/s41599-024-04272-y Network) and PubMed repositories from 2016 to 2024.",
    "The subsequent sections delineate the principal discoveries, illustrative practices, robustness, constraints of the TPD programs under review, and recommendations for forthcoming STEM TPD endeavours.",
    "While the findings of this study are grounded in the Chinese context, the implications extend beyond national borders.",
    "Many of the challenges observed in China, such as regional disparities in STEM TPD access and the need for interdisciplinary skills, resonate with global concerns about STEM education."
